>    splitting legacy `sampler2D`. specmap_bump samples `normalMap` before `diffuseMap` â†’ normalMap=t0,
>    diffuseMap=t1, opposite the engine's D3D9 stage-index SRV bind â†’ the blue normal map was sampled as
