codex
The first important distinction is visible now: LOD is chosen inside `SkeletalAppearance2::render()` from a projected screen diameter, while `CharacterLodManager` separately assigns per-character throttles and hard-skinning pressure by distance order. I’m reading the surrounding blocks to capture the exact thresholds and side effects.
