1149-
1150-		In multi stream rendering, the skinned components (position, normal,
1151-		dot3 if present) are skinned directly into a dynamic vertex buffer.  The
1152-		non-skinned, constant components (color and non-dot3 texture coordinates)
1153-		are stored in a per-instance static buffer.
1154-
1155-		In single stream rendering, the skinned components (position, normal,
1156-		dot3 if present) are skinned in a common system vertex buffer.  The
1157-		non-skinned, constant components (color and non-dot3 texture coordinates) are
1158-		stored in an instance system buffer.  The dynamic vertex buffer
1159-		contains the full set of vertex information and is constructed by
1160-		merging skinned common system vertex buffer with the constant component
1161-		system vertex buffer.
1162-	*/
